            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1692361414220-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the aubergine is browning, peel and chop your<strong> red onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and roughly chop</p><p>Add the <strong>onion wedges </strong>and <strong>chopped pepper</strong> to the dish and stir it all together</p>",
