      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the ratatouille is cooking, add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong>, the <strong>remaining dried oregano </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> with 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p><p>Cover tightly with <strong>tin foil</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 30 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>herby rice</strong></p>",
